of the Northwest of England,

00:48:36.970 --> 00:48:38.880 align:middle line:84%
who wanted to devote
her life to good works.

00:48:38.880 --> 00:48:44.220 align:middle line:90%


00:48:44.220 --> 00:48:47.110 align:middle line:84%
Noyal had promised
herself to God,

00:48:47.110 --> 00:48:51.000 align:middle line:84%
but her father wanted her to
