As Noyal rejected his
advances and his gifts,

00:49:16.970 --> 00:49:18.200 align:middle line:90%
Nisan had her beheaded.

00:49:18.200 --> 00:49:27.970 align:middle line:90%


00:49:27.970 --> 00:49:33.060 align:middle line:84%
>> As the sword fell onto
her neck, a miracle happened.

00:49:33.060 --> 00:49:35.000 align:middle line:10%
Instead of falling
to the ground,

00:49:35.000 --> 00:49:38.280 align:middle line:10%
Noyal took her head and her
