00:50:30.560 --> 00:50:38.490 align:middle line:90%


00:50:38.490 --> 00:50:42.510 align:middle line:84%
>> Man will never have a
simple relationship with water,

00:50:42.510 --> 00:50:45.720 align:middle line:84%
because it is a great
part of himself.

00:50:45.720 --> 00:50:48.150 align:middle line:90%
Because it is many things.

00:50:48.150 --> 00:50:51.150 align:middle line:84%
Because it is charged with
contradictory symbolism.

00:50:51.150 --> 00:50:56.050 align:middle line:90%


00:50:56.050 --> 00:51:00.610 align:middle line:84%
Because from the very
beginning, water is transformed.

00:51:00.610 --> 00:51:04.690 align:middle line:84%
It changes its nature,
